room_title: Escape room "The Reporter" by Brainstorm Escape Room Bonita Springs in Fort Myers
room_description: You are an investigative reporter doing a story on secret societies. An informant lets you into a highly classified and isolated government facility that monitors them. While searching the main office to find a contact name, date and place of next meeting you set off an alarm. You have 75 minutes until government forces surround the facility.
